{
  "stem": "1222.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I told him which way to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He walked almost the whole night, dragging me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We went, and I had no other choice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Otherwise, I would be dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I figured, let's take a chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Here, I'm giving you the instruction what you have to take chances.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You have to be very fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Is far but food, up till today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When we used to have a piece of bread-- and I swear with my life-- my Manek used to chew the piece of bread, the same piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Before swallowing the piece of bread-- many times it happened-- he used to take out the piece of bread and put it in there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said, Shmuelik, [SOBBING] you need it more than me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You can't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He didn't want to swallow that, he used to give it to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's the answer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's why he's crying right now in Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But he memorized all that stuff that we're talking about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the shooting was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Heavy shooting, very heavy shooting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were fighting every bridges, they were fighting in our city by the water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when it stopped-- the shooting-- and we were still there, we knew they were pushed back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't give up, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Rovno was smashed, about 80% of the buildings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Rovno has got 300,000 Jews-- that's 40 miles from Mezhyrich.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were fighting there, I would say about two weeks, that's the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were pushed back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No-- even when I was-- after that, and then city after city, they would kill-- I mean, they lost a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
